author: Thoughty2
description: In 1990, two hikers near the Scottish village of Calvine captured what’s been called the clearest UFO photo ever taken — a massive diamond-shaped object hovering silently in the sky. The image vanished into Ministry of Defence archives, locked away until 2076. Was it a secret military craft, or something not of this world?
title: The Calvine UFO: Britain’s Strangest Unsolved Mystery
